          "_name": "pricing03",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"pricing03\" group=\"Pricing\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n  <mbr-parameters>\n    <header>Size</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n    <header>Show/Hide</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showTitle\" title=\"Title\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showSubtitle\" title=\"Subtitle\">\n    <select title=\"Columns\" name=\"columns\">\n      <option value=\"6\">2</option>\n      <option value=\"4\" selected>3</option>\n      <option value=\"3\">4</option>\n    </select>\n    <header>Card</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showCardTitle\" title=\"Title\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showCardSubtitle\" title=\"Subtitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showText\" title=\"Text\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showList\" title=\"List\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showButtons\" title=\"Buttons\" checked>\n    <header>Color</header>\n    <input type=\"color\" name=\"cardsHead\" title=\"Head\" value=\"#232323\">\n    <input type=\"color\" name=\"cardsBg\" title=\"BG\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    <input type=\"color\" name=\"iconColor\" title=\"Icon Color\" value=\"#4caf50\">\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <fieldset type=\"background\" parallax name=\"bg\" required>\n      <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n      <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n    </fieldset>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#fafafa\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type == 'image'\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.1\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type == 'image'\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n\n  <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\"></div>\n  <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n      <div class=\"col-12 content-head\">\n        <div class=\"mbr-section-head mb-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showSubtitle\">\n          <h4 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n            <b>Serviços</b><br></h4>\n          <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mt-4 mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.\n          </h5>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"row\">\n      \n      \n      <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}} item-mb active\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"item-head\">\n            <h5 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\"><b>Sensibilização em IA</b><div><b>in Company</b></div></h5>\n            <h6 class=\"item-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-subtitle\" mbr-if=\"showCardSubtitle\">sob demanda</h6>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"item-content\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardSubtitle || showText || showButtons\">\n            <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\"><b>COURSE PACKAGE + MENTORIA\n<br>INTELIGÊNCIA ARTIFICIAL</b><br></p>\n            <div class=\"mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showList && showText\"></div>\n            <div class=\"counter-container mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article mbr-if=\"showList\">\n              <ul>\n                <li><b>Código: </b>CPKMENIA 401\n</li><li><b>Público-alvo: </b>Gestores e equipes internas\n</li><li><b>Carga horária: </b>16&nbsp;horas\n</li><li><b>Modelo: </b>Presencial | Online</li><li><b>Módulos: </b>Mentoria + Conceitos Básicos (CBIA 101 + Hands on (CBIA 102)  + acompanhamento.\n</li><li><b>Recursos: </b>Customização de Conteúdos | Acesso a canais exclusivos de conteúdos | Rodada de estudos práticos | Acesso online aos materiais dos cursos | Certificados de participação.\n</li><li><b>Ideal para: </b>Empresas\n</li><li><i>Instalações do cliente | Base SP | Fora da base, custos de alimentação, viagem e estada do instrutor serão de responsabilidade do cliente.\n</i></li><li><b>Turma mínima de 10 alunos.</b></li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer \" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a href=\"mailto:ceo.ojohn@gmail.com\" class=\"btn item-btn btn-black-outline\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Solicite sua cotação</a></div>\n        </div>\n      </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}} item-mb\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"item-head\">\n            <h5 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\"><b>Mentoria</b><br><b>in Company</b></h5>\n            <h6 class=\"item-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-subtitle\" mbr-if=\"showCardSubtitle\">sob demanda</h6>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"item-content\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardSubtitle || showText || showButtons\">\n            <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\"><b>SERVICE PACK</b><br><b>INTELIGÊNCIA ARTIFICIAL</b></p>\n            <div class=\"mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showList && showText\"></div>\n            <div class=\"counter-container mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article mbr-if=\"showList\">\n              <ul>\n                <li><b>Código: </b>SPKMENIA 501</li><li><b>Público-alvo: </b>Gestores e equipes internas</li><li><b>Carga horária:</b>&nbsp;mínimo de 08 horas&nbsp;</li><li><b>Modelo: </b>Presencial | Online</li><li>\n</li><li><b>Módulos: </b>Mentoria e&nbsp; acompanhamento.</li><li><b style=\"font-size: calc(1rem + 0 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">Recursos: </b><span style=\"font-size: calc(1rem + 0 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">consultoria especializada.</span><br></li><li><i style=\"font-size: calc(1rem + 0 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">Instalações do cliente | Base SP | Fora da base, custos de alimentação, viagem e estada do mentor serão de responsabilidade do cliente.</i><br></li><li><i>A carga horária é estimada e mínima, caso haja necessidade de mais horas, será previamente acordado com o cliente.</i></li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer \" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a href=\"mailto:ceo.ojohn@gmail.com\" class=\"btn item-btn btn-black-outline\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Solicite sua cotação</a></div>\n        </div>\n      </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}} item-mb\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"item-head\">\n            <h5 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\"><b>Super apps as a service</b></h5>\n            <h6 class=\"item-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-subtitle\" mbr-if=\"showCardSubtitle\">sob demanda</h6>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"item-content\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardSubtitle || showText || showButtons\">\n            <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\"><b>SERVICE PACK</b><br><b>super apps as a service</b></p>\n            <div class=\"mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showList && showText\"></div>\n            <div class=\"counter-container mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article mbr-if=\"showList\">\n              <ul>\n                <li><b>Código: </b>SPKSAASIA 601</li><li><b>Público-alvo: </b>Gestores&nbsp;</li><li><b>Carga horária:</b>&nbsp;mínimo de 40 horas de desenvolvimento</li><li><b>Modelo: </b>subscrição mensal de uso</li><li>\n</li><li><b>Escopo: </b>desenvolvimento da solução a ser definida com o cliente.&nbsp;</li><li><b style=\"font-size: calc(1rem + 0 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">Recursos: </b><span style=\"font-size: calc(1rem + 0 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">desenvolvimento e serviços em </span>nuvem<span style=\"font-size: calc(1rem + 0 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">.</span><br></li><li><i style=\"font-size: calc(1rem + 0 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\"><b>50% de desconto </b>na Subscrição mensal do <b>IA Compara</b>.</i><br></li><li><i>Instalações do cliente | Base SP | Fora da base, custos de alimentação, viagem e estada do desenvolvedor serão de responsabilidade do cliente.</i></li><li><i>A carga horária é estimada e mínima, caso haja necessidade de mais horas, será previamente acordado com o cliente.</i></li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer \" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a href=\"mailto:ceo.ojohn@gmail.com\" class=\"btn item-btn btn-black-outline\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Solicite sua cotação</a></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "uRUjqrLHXW",
          "_anchor": "pricing03-1l",
          "_protectedParams": [],
